sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
	 
    Note right of browser: User inputs new note into HTML element: <input type="name" name="note">
    Note right of browser: User clicks on 'Save' button (or tab + enter key)
    Note right of browser: User's note is added to the page BEFORE sending to server (potential for desync here)

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: 201: {"message":"note created"}
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: if there are any errors here a page refresh may cause the new note to disappear